Well, we have an editorial board, which consists of David McKittrick, he's a librarian at Trinity College, Cambridge, Alan Bell, who's the librarian of the Rhodes House Library at Oxford, and Ted Hoffman, who used to be an independent bookseller, but is now with Bernard Quaritch, and Steve Weissman at Simones.

00:36.835 --> 00:43.162
